# Studio naming (do not confuse repos)

| You mean | Use | Never call it |
|----------|-----|----------------|
| **Li World Studio** (product brand) | User-facing name in docs | A repo slug |
| **Editor / demo / mockups** | Repo **`li-studio-app`** | `li-world-studio`, “the studio repo” |
| **`import studio`** API | Repo **`li-studio`** (package) | The application |
| **`import world`** ECS | Repo **`li-world`** | The editor |

```bash
# Bootstrap application repo from lic (one-time)
./scripts/bootstrap-li-studio-app-repo.sh ../li-studio-app
```

**Canonical doc:** `docs/ecosystem/studio-naming.md`
